My name is KAHKI. My Animal ID # is A1020884.
I am a female brown and white pit bull mix. The shelter thinks I am about 1 YEAR 6 MONTHS old.  A volunteer writes: Khaki always shows how happy she is to see someone with a leash......she wiggles, her tail wags, and she sits right up front ready to be leashed for an outing. She's so happy to be out to explore, pulling on the leash to get from point A to point B as there is simply so much to see and sniff! She lets me put a coat on her as it's cold, and she's stealing kisses from me when I lean down . We head to the backyard where she can be free off leash, and she promptly shows me her sit when I offer a treat. She keeps sitting, I keep giving her treats which she takes softly and we're buddies! Her soft caramel eyes match her coat, and she looks into mine with gentleness. Her forehead gets those adorable wrinkles that I want to smooth away and tell her life will be good. As we play she gets the zoomies and it's adorable to watch her run around the pen in happiness. Such a good girl! When some energy is spent she happily comes into my lap for some snuggle time and we huddle together to stay warm. Khaki is looking for a new family where she will be pampered and loved and be the perfect companion she was meant to be. Ask to meet Khaki today.
